query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 1 AND q.favorite_count <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('ansible',
'centos',
'cross-platform',
'duplicates',
'find',
'interface-builder',
'jquery-validate',
'nunit',
'pinvoke',
'segmentation-fault',
'unity-container',
'vb6',
'web-config',
'xmlhttprequest');
